{"tid":1420346,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對連登記者會日後少少意見 （不喜就插，吸納意見）","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:55.000Z","uid":31721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7938d4450434cd2139adc99f61359257863dbc34","tid":1420346,"uid":31721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"首先想講，開記者會係一個非常唔錯嘅開始！但就記者嘅問題，其實可以反映到我地日後改善嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n開記者會嘅目的係發放市民或示威者嘅訴求、反駁政府歪理等等。固此，我建議可以參考美國白宮聯署，提出一啲嘅意見，並用文宣去引更多市民簽名認同，從而達到提高認受性。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為如果依家要搞記者會，今日答得算好，但有不足之處，因為時間問題攞唔到太多民意。但要搞就一定要搞得好好睇睇，要比社會（尤其果班中產）睇到，究竟比起一個中央控制嘅港府出黎 同一個「民主」系統而出嘅記者會係一個咩質素，睇大家有個比較。民主總比起欽點好！<br />\n<br />\n如果連登可以整一個聯署網，咁就好，不論藍定黃，都係果到簽，睇到個民意，呢個記者會就變得更紮實，更多姿多彩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我講野廢，如果有咩覺得可以講多啲或有其他嘅意見，都係樓下講啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永不割席</span> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}